AntiAddictionStrings.client_Login_StopPlayingDialog_DialogTex: According to selective shutdown, you can't play the game at the current time. Disconnecting.
AntiAddictionStrings.client_Login_AntiAddictionDialog_Text_de: Excessive gameplay can interfere with normal daily life. {hour} hours have passed since you started playing.
AntiAddictionStrings.client_Login_AntiAddictionDialog_Text_Sh: In order to comply with shutdown law, game play and login will be terminated after a while.
